rune 2024-02-11 3:04 AM
Ok here's the rundown of Floppy Fish for people who ask In 2014 Adam posted a short story to his tumblr along with a short song snippet. This short snippet was dubbed "Floppy Fish", but it's actual name is "Trust Me" according to the song metadata. Recently I got everyone to spam "Release Floppy Fish" in Adam's insta comments which has sort of amplified the demand for the full song - to the point where Adam himself has acknowledged it after almost 10 years. That's why people keep talking about it. There are a few fan songs based on it, namely Lynz' rendition of it - these are not the full song, no more than the 30 seconds in the original Tumblr post has ever been released.
